{"tid":648943,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[分手]同港女女朋友落bar玩點知俾佢鬧咗一餐，好撚無辜","createTime":"2018-05-01T07:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T19:28:38.000Z","uid":97606,"like":7,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7435378a3d5bda248a9cdd2939a5b530788e8a38","tid":648943,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:07:36.000Z","msg":"早幾日見放工無嘢做就同條女落bar，<br />\n飲咗兩杯high high哋就落咗舞池，<br />\n見到有條鬼妹身材幾正個樣又掂，<br />\n咪過去磨下佢囉。<br />\n<br />\n點知條衰妹唔抗拒不突止，<br />\n仲要趌高個屎忽起勢咁磨我條撚，<br />\n完全當我哋隔離無人望住咁樣。<br />\n我見到咁即刻唔執輸，<br />\n一嘢拉佢個頭過嚟攬實佢un佢個大蘿友，<br />\n一路聞佢啲頭髮香一路喺後面摸佢對大波，<br />\n原來條衰妹無帶bra，兩粒的仲要又漲又彈，<br />\n我隔住件衫一路掃佢兩粒lin，一路聽住條女用唔知咩文喺到淫叫，<br />\n呢個時候我女朋友無啦啦走咗過嚟打我一巴，<br />\n條鬼妹見到即時彈開呆咗，喺到話:What the fuck?<br />\n我即時爆粗罵條女問佢做乜鳩，<br />\n佢喊晒口咁話我背叛佢，走去搞其他女人。<br />\n<br />\n但係事實上我同條鬼妹都未有肉體上接觸，<br />\n我褲都未除，淨係隔住件衫摸兩下都話唔俾，<br />\n其實我淨係等於摸咗塊布喳喎，咁又點叫背叛你呢小姐？<br />\n打到呢到真係覺得好撚委屈，諗住今晚返去扑多佢幾次就同佢講分手，各位手足點睇？"},{"pid":"e8cc1fa009385044f5ae67884303cb07f12bd012","tid":648943,"uid":43653,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6980f8c9f670a720f67be6642c2717c3d94d6f09","tid":648943,"uid":97606,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8cc1fa009385044f5ae67884303cb07f12bd012","tid":648943,"uid":43653,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係條女戇鳩姐"},{"pid":"9c98a29f76397bc4d593a82117e8a773527e0201","tid":648943,"uid":67201,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:11:25.000Z","msg":"唔好咁多性幻想ok?"},{"pid":"8c39336c58d9759499e5dee9d267ee4f30999375","tid":648943,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c98a29f76397bc4d593a82117e8a773527e0201","tid":648943,"uid":67201,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:11:25.000Z","msg":"唔好咁多性幻想ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"真人真事"},{"pid":"1cafb262cd2f3bd3c6c77e19bfe751384a8dbadd","tid":648943,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a625ca24374269e5be50a7489d10fea8ea546713","tid":648943,"uid":100103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"叫翻條女落舞池俾鬼佬摸翻兩下當打和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b97514024b5115c6fcbc443bdd271ef58148a5","tid":648943,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"a625ca24374269e5be50a7489d10fea8ea546713","tid":648943,"uid":100103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"叫翻條女落舞池俾鬼佬摸翻兩下當打和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:14:49.000Z","msg":"佢條臭閪有撚鬼佬要咩<br />\n我肯屌下佢已經執到啦"},{"pid":"1b580317ead33ff15b8ba3534152ff8269957bdf","tid":648943,"uid":27247,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/151617_1c2026bf518c0dff182b4312643fc939.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F151617_1c2026bf518c0dff182b4312643fc939.gif&h=d94e6877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bfbf364c533186ec6bb028297affcea5f2222d1","tid":648943,"uid":53554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:16:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90915d5e8895e831520b83ce9dc4089fb786712f","tid":648943,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9ecd69a03569e11f01c085cda